{
  "stem": "26765.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She took care of the German Jewish children, because we spoke German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she was a German nun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she took care of me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And sometimes I wanted to run away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I told her, I'm not staying here anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When I got angry, when somebody tried to dress me, or so-- you know, I wanted to dress myself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she would say, well, where are you going?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'd say, I'm going to my aunt in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm taking my tricycle with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she'd gave me a big box.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would pick my things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that would be about as far as I got.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was also a-- a priest at the convent who was in charge there, who took a special interest in my brother and me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he wrote my mother in German-- always.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother always wrote to us beautiful picture cards with fairytale scenes of or And he would read them to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he asked my mother if he could baptize us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she wrote a letter to the bishop in 's-Hertogenbosch, which is the-- the largest-- next largest city in that part of Holland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she gave her permission to have us baptized.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, they were very happy to have us baptized, because people of the Catholic faith believe that if you're not baptized, you're going to spend the rest of your life-- your eternal life-- in-- in hell.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Rector Wijers baptized us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But even before he baptized us, he paid special attention to my brother and me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know exactly why, except that I was the youngest child there, and maybe that was the reason.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he would invite us to the rectory to have dinner with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
